				\begin{document}$$(1\overline{1}0)$$\end{document} plane of MoS2 [93], and slight changes of valence and conduction bands upon introduction of adsorbate state in bandgap by oxidizing gases (O2, NO, and NO2) [86] were observed. Therefore, exploration on active sites, adsorbate states, and band characteristics change during the gas sensing are needed to further understand the sensing mechanism of MoS2 FETs.
